Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.42,0:03:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是總倒下啊 中村
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.28,0:03:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笹原 你為什麼又翹了掃除啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.68,0:03:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把我自己的區域掃除過了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.06,0:03:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有很多沒掃乾淨的灰塵哦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.39,0:03:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.69,0:03:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點回到你那片區域去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.61,0:03:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個 你為什麼知道我在屋頂呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.74,0:03:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼蠢話！！？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.91,0:03:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不過是被這晴天吸引來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.36,0:03:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾溜躂溜躂順便經過而已的！！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.16,0:03:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.83,0:03:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你特意費心真是抱歉吶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.67,0:03:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然還幫忙看了我的區域
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.55,0:03:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可不要誤會哦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.05,0:03:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是為了你吶！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.60,0:04:09.61,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs70\pos(1200,360)\fad(520,520)\blur10\bord2}抓\N娃\N娃\N機
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.42,0:04:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息日
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.00,0:04:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和麻衣約好了去鄰市見面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.92,0:04:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像能免費得到點心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.76,0:04:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要吃到爽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.26,0:04:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃麵包嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.72,0:04:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.05,0:04:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出來的時候吃過了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.60,0:04:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狗啊… 怎麼說呢… 有點犯規 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.15,0:04:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.65,0:04:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.99,0:04:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎喲 就快要到了 要不要站起來吶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.95,0:04:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.74,0:05:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}下一站
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.58,0:05:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs42}時定問屋町
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.29,0:05:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs42}時定問屋町
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.29,0:05:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好時機！！播音員！！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.42,0:05:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs42}時定問屋町
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.92,0:05:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs42}時定問屋町到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.00,0:05:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.67,0:05:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.88,0:05:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}請於右側下車
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.51,0:05:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車內的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.26,0:05:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.18,0:05:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛嘛嘛… 應該是從這邊說再見吶！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.19,0:05:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍住忍住
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.11,0:05:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種程度就要驚慌失措可不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.82,0:05:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.24,0:05:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有點那個急事！！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.82,0:05:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～～真是的！！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.03,0:05:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.91,0:05:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正是再也不會見面的小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.62,0:05:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正是鄰市
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.66,0:05:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都不認識我吶！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.50,0:05:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在意不要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.29,0:05:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…話說怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.71,0:05:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在跟著我？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.01,0:05:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯覺錯覺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.51,0:05:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天稍微有點過敏吶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.13,0:05:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.93,0:06:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前不是說出了車站就有一個大工漢堡店麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.47,0:06:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.02,0:06:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣給我畫的地圖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.68,0:06:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得 軟趴趴的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.64,0:06:12.52,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs30\frz19.381\pos(378,275)}大工\N漢堡店
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.64,0:06:12.52,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs30\frz19.381\pos(424,458)}在這
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.10,0:06:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要趕緊問路嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.77,0:06:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.86,0:06:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.27,0:06:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.15,0:06:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大工漢堡店在哪…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.94,0:06:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我… 我說！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.65,0:06:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼從剛才開始就一直跟著我！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.20,0:06:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事會那什麼喲！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.11,0:06:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,著作權會怎麼樣的喲！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.91,0:06:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大工漢堡店的話就在這後面哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.49,0:06:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要在那裡跟別人碰面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.58,0:06:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話我帶你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.01,0:06:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.89,0:06:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.89,0:06:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社團活動的原因遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.80,0:06:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.64,0:06:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的跟別人碰面啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.93,0:06:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.69,0:06:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣還沒來呢嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.69,0:06:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.11,0:06:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是倒霉日嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.69,0:07:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意想不到的丟人啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.99,0:07:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 算了吧 反正是鄰市…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.12,0:07:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 樂觀的看的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.37,0:07:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在好的層面上這也算是人生的預先演習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.66,0:07:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 這份羞恥我會跨越過去的！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.38,0:07:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是什麼我都會跨越過去的！！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.34,0:07:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小祐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.80,0:07:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.80,0:07:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.76,0:07:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個… 難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.05,0:07:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Trick or Treat
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.31,0:07:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…這樣的話 那就沒辦法了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.39,0:07:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了得到點心…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.06,0:07:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我上了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.23,0:07:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Trick or Treat
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.56,0:07:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬聖節是上周哦
