Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.03,0:07:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs54\bord4\shad0\blur8\fad(500,500)\c&H000000&\pos(367,100)}從\N嚇\N唬\N人\N的\N烏\N鴉\N旁\N邊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.03,0:07:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs54\bord4\shad0\blur8\fad(500,500)\c&H000000&\pos(60,100)}經\N過\N的\N時\N候
