Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.83,0:07:54.79,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx95\pos(1100,550)\bord3\3c&HF9FAFD&}雪\N飄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.83,0:07:54.79,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial\fs27\pos(1172,546)\bord3\3c&HF9FAFD&}flsnow
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.33,0:07:58.59,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs100\pos(800,360)\fad(520,0)\shad3\4c&H040200&\c&HF0F3F2&}睡\N\N覺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.13,0:08:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺不太困
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.30,0:08:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說數跳過柵欄的羊的數量的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.01,0:08:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能睡著了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.22,0:08:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白啦 我試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.27,0:08:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一隻羊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.44,0:08:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才一隻就睡著了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.27,0:08:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士好厲害！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.65,0:08:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.19,0:08:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一隻…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.40,0:08:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羊 還沒跳過去呢吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.61,0:08:27.45,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs60\pos(760,360)\fad(520,0)\shad2\4c&H040200&\c&HF1F1F1&}志\N願\N精\N神
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.87,0:08:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.08,0:08:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝了 不愧是姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.25,0:08:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 這種事情 是笹原同學教給你的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.21,0:08:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為 為什麼我非得讓他手把手的教啊？！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.18,0:08:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 你們關係很好的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.68,0:08:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不哦 根本不！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.05,0:08:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豈止是根本不 簡直就是根本不哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.10,0:08:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.89,0:08:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是之前不是幫他熨手帕來得麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.31,0:08:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是偶然在路上撿到的垃圾而已罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.36,0:09:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？ 是因為是笹原同學的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.90,0:09:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了不是那麼回事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.07,0:09:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是因為想要鍛煉手臂肌肉的時候 正好看到那個熨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.07,0:09:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面湊巧有那塊手帕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.04,0:09:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之類的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.41,0:09:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之類的事情啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.21,0:09:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好容易看穿…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.92,0:09:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是姐姐 你熨手帕的時候那麼高興來的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.84,0:09:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼蠢話啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.97,0:09:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那… 那個時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.34,0:09:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候 只是因為地球進入了光子帶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.45,0:09:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 聽我說 昨天啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.24,0:09:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.24,0:09:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和大野君說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.58,0:09:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.42,0:10:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電車坐了兩小時
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.42,0:10:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客車坐了一小時
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.34,0:10:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠離了都市的人山人海
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.84,0:10:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 終於來到了這偏僻的S村
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.36,0:10:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.11,0:10:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然心想著可能此生再也找不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.11,0:10:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我仍然不能完全放棄 那本很久以前就開始找尋的書
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.54,0:10:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將我那灰色的少女時代
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.41,0:10:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塗上了繽紛的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.79,0:10:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被稱作如夢似幻的那本書
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.71,0:10:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在這 圖書館裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.26,0:10:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個時代 能讀到那本書
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.02,0:11:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對和贈書人有著這樣的機緣心懷著感激之情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.53,0:11:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拿著那本書
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.57,0:11:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按捺著心中的激動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.54,0:11:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.96,0:11:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢的開啟了這本書
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.92,0:11:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\c&HD6A6FE&\pos(622,498)}與愛有關的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.42,0:11:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 時間快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.55,0:11:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都確認一下寫沒寫名字哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.55,0:11:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.76,0:11:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.02,0:11:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.18,0:11:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.35,0:11:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6——
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.48,0:11:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5——
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.44,0:11:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4——
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.44,0:11:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3——
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.69,0:11:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2——…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.07,0:11:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1——
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.37,0:11:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.24,0:12:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 那請大家從後面傳上來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.64,0:12:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬聖節 早就結束了哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.99,0:12:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這咖啡 有點不像咖啡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.49,0:12:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？ 不像咖啡？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.79,0:12:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.87,0:12:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我自己也不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.96,0:12:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說好呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.87,0:12:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是不像咖啡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.00,0:12:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說啦 你嘗嘗看？ 來來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.29,0:12:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 不像咖啡什麼的是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.34,0:12:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像咖啡！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.69,0:13:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.52,0:13:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於完成啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.11,0:13:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是Biscuit 2號
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.90,0:13:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是Biscuit 2號
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.57,0:13:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊… 前段時間的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.24,0:13:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反應 好冷淡！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.83,0:13:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 我想讓你好好看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.54,0:13:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 之前我們也看過了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.41,0:13:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1號和2號是不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.79,0:13:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更加 更～加厲害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.84,0:13:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是Biscuit 2號
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.92,0:13:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是東雲博士做的Biscuit機器人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.01,0:13:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就如名字一樣 動力源是餅乾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.64,0:13:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了餅乾 我就能夠勞動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.10,0:13:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士 差不多該給我餅乾…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.19,0:13:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.31,0:13:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是最後一個了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.91,0:14:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Biscuit 2號的特技是速讀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.58,0:14:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.41,0:14:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.50,0:14:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.21,0:14:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不吃驚呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.87,0:14:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 我也能速讀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.00,0:14:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 為什麼總是讀得磨磨蹭蹭的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.17,0:14:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.26,0:14:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有普通人的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.14,0:14:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼了？ Biscuit 2號
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.27,0:14:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書上文字太多了 有點犯困吶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.73,0:14:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是有點普通的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.07,0:14:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不說好厲害！！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.78,0:14:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明博士非常厲害！！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.49,0:14:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 因為那種事情生氣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.16,0:14:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是那種事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.48,0:14:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬要說 博士從一開始就非常厲害的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.33,0:14:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 博士我好像有點搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.37,0:14:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得並不是搞錯了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.46,0:14:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶吶 博士有多麼厲害？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.13,0:14:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 可能是秩父連山程度的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.13,0:15:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那根本聽不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.47,0:15:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 那納拉伯平原之類的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.47,0:15:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 更大點的比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.68,0:15:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 鯨魚之類的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.39,0:15:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 可能是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.06,0:15:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為鯨魚很大吶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.69,0:15:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很大吶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.27,0:15:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,900)\pos(652,493)\c&H0A0A0A&\shad0\bord0\K100}隻{\K100}言{\K100}片{\K100}語
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.53,0:15:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有「那樣就行」之類的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.33,0:15:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有「這樣就行」之類的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.04,0:15:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.84,0:15:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 準備了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.51,0:15:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我準備了雙六
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.93,0:15:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 準備了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.05,0:15:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我準備了猜謎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.39,0:15:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜謎的話 和和氣氣的很有趣的吧！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.01,0:15:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 讓公主開心的話就能得到一筆錢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.93,0:15:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是很有意思的娛樂活動吶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.31,0:15:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不時常有些樂趣可受不了的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.36,0:15:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.36,0:16:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才 球是放進了這邊的 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.95,0:16:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際是 在這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.20,0:16:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯啊 66號
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.16,0:16:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然有這種特技啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.41,0:16:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上 偷偷的以王室專屬魔術師為目標來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.29,0:16:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是那樣的話 你可就安寧了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.21,0:16:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.88,0:16:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 我燃起來了哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.46,0:16:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要得到那一筆錢！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.30,0:16:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦誒 時間到了哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.98,0:16:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.85,0:16:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs45\bord0\shad0\pos(751,170)\frz354.392\c&H0E171D&}侍\N從
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.19,0:16:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 按照剛才發下去的簽的順序開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.61,0:16:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿到一號的人 上前來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.44,0:16:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從我開始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.82,0:16:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 直接就從66號開始嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.36,0:16:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這肯定要拿那筆錢了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.32,0:16:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,專屬魔術師嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.37,0:16:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住你的夢想哦 66號！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.33,0:16:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 好厲害！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.00,0:16:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.42,0:17:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 球在哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.51,0:17:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要成為 專屬魔術師…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.01,0:17:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.52,0:17:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿到二號的人 上前來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.64,0:17:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於要到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.81,0:17:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將我的名聲讓世人知道的時刻！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.65,0:17:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我把這危機化為機會！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.48,0:17:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}誰啊 哦誒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.53,0:17:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.74,0:17:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽默的四號
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.99,0:17:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.32,0:17:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的大笑話的話肯定能行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.32,0:17:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四號 請允許我來演出
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.50,0:17:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.80,0:17:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}拿到三號的人 上前來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.46,0:17:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到… 竟然連四號
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.88,0:17:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦誒 沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.80,0:17:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輪到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.64,0:17:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才說 猜謎什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.10,0:17:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完蛋啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.22,0:17:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到竟然會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.89,0:17:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我的長處就只有猜謎了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.85,0:18:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此時一定要讓公主說出正確答案…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.15,0:18:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 絕對不允許出錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.03,0:18:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要出一個特別簡單的問題…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.57,0:18:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我是6號
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.07,0:18:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請允許我給公主出個謎！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.20,0:18:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖… 雖說是麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.25,0:18:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不能吃的麵包是什～～麼吶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.34,0:18:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個問題有兩個選項！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.42,0:18:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1是煎鍋 2是菠蘿包
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.42,0:18:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}煎鍋：日文中即為Fry Pan的日式念法，Pan與日文的麵包同音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.38,0:18:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 是哪項！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.01,0:18:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.56,0:18:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.90,0:18:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這 這是正確答案！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.61,0:18:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.15,0:18:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫無悔恨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.65,0:18:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才怪！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.08,0:18:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完蛋啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.16,0:18:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連猜謎大師也滾蛋啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.37,0:18:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.33,0:18:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我… 我是七號
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.50,0:19:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請允許我說一下全部的奧運會舉辦城市
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.13,0:19:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.17,0:19:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的勇氣 我們不會忘記的哦 七號！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.72,0:19:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.76,0:19:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有誰能夠讓公主高興麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.51,0:19:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.89,0:19:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來想來啦啦隊女孩的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.48,0:19:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你個笨蛋 我還準備用屁股折斷一次性筷子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.35,0:19:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我準備來南京玉簾的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.35,0:19:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs42}南京玉簾：日本的一種街頭表演
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.19,0:19:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是要來把捲心菜切成細絲的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.44,0:19:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們全員… 都要被消滅了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.20,0:19:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦誒哦誒…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.50,0:19:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我忘了的話可不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.75,0:19:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.88,0:19:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那副詼諧的樣子就能看出來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.63,0:19:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是幽默屆無人能出其右的諧星
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.76,0:19:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詼諧13
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.76,0:19:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\pos(689,656)}Thirteen
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.47,0:19:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我來一個起死回生的表演
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.30,0:19:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改變一下這場面的氣氛吧！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.22,0:20:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 13號！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.60,0:20:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎麼說都太危險了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.90,0:20:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們還以為我只是來跳一支天鵝湖的舞的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.36,0:20:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 仔細看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.16,0:20:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的幽默這種東西由我來教給…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.41,0:20:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.56,0:20:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吧——！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.79,0:20:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詼諧13～～！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.79,0:20:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\pos(597,656)}Thirteen
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.25,0:20:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧…為什麼連我都…！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.13,0:20:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 五號
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.50,0:20:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想讓我們等到什麼時候啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.80,0:20:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快出來！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.63,0:20:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.17,0:20:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五號那傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.09,0:20:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.80,0:20:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.13,0:20:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是！！ 這是我帽子的號啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.97,0:20:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.80,0:20:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.47,0:20:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦… 哦誒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.60,0:20:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五號 不是你麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.35,0:20:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完蛋啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.19,0:20:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦誒 五號！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.23,0:20:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多趕緊出來吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.44,0:20:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是哪個傢伙！？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.62,0:21:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒！！？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.49,0:21:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.50,0:21:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個 誰都可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.66,0:21:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快來！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.75,0:21:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.58,0:21:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼掙扎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.71,0:21:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.17,0:21:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完蛋啦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.23,0:21:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.31,0:21:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管有幾條命 都不夠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.69,0:21:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種任性的娛樂活動…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.86,0:21:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊玩兒蛋去吧！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.84,0:21:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去走廊裡站著
